Text: RE AgreementThank you for sending your GISB agreement I have forwarded it onto AK Steel for them to review and sign However in the meantime it has been brought my attention that there is a master agreement in place between AK Steel and Enron North America If this is the case then we can work off of the master agreement Please let me know if you know of a master agreement already in existence Thank you Julie Julie Wentz Bid Coordinator EnergyGatewaycom ext This message including any attachments contains confidential information intended for a specific individual and purpose and is protected by law If you are not the intended recipient you should delete this message and are hereby notified that any disclosure copying or distribution of this message or the taking of any action based on it is strictly prohibited Please call with any questions Original Message From mailto Sent Friday December PM To Subject Agreement Julie Further to our conversation please see the attached GISB draft for your review See attached file A K Steel GISBdoc Regards Debra Perlingiere Enron North America Corp Legal Department Smith Street EB Houston Texas Phone Fax
